             <string/>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="label_allPopupLayoutsExplanation">
            <property name="text">
             <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Set all the layouts for the Popup mode - one layout per line.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Valid formats:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;WxH&lt;/span&gt;] - an W column wide and H rows high grid layout (example 4x2 will give 2 rows with 4 columns each for a total of 8 tiles)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;X,Y,Width,Height&lt;/span&gt;] - an Width wide and Height tall tile located at X and Y coordinates (example 20,10,400px,200px for a 400 pixel wide, 200 pixel high tile placed at 20% screen width and 10% screen height)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;[&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;X,Y,Width,Height,AnchorX,AnchorY&lt;/span&gt;] - same as above, except tile is placed using the tile anchor point (example 50,50,320px,240px,CENTER,CENTER to place a 320x240 pixel large tile in the middle of the screen - without the CENTER anchor, the top-left corner would end up in the middle of the screen instead)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Width&lt;/span&gt; and &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Height&lt;/span&gt; can be in percent (usually between 0 and 100, decimal values supported - recommended), pixels (absolute values using px suffix - not recommended) and fractions (e.g. 1/3).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;AnchorX&lt;/span&gt; can be a percentage (e.g. 50%) or fraction (e.g. 1/2) of tile Width or one of &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;LEFT&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;CENTER&lt;/span&gt; or &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;RIGHT&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;AnchorY&lt;/span&gt; can be a percentage (e.g. 50%) or fraction (e.g. 1/2) of tile Height or one of &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;TOP&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;CENTER&lt;/span&gt; or &lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;BOTTOM&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The layout can be made of multiple grids and/or tiles separated by a + (example 0,0,50,100+50,0,50,100 which is equal to a 2x1 grid).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can also use one of these special layouts: SPECIAL_FILL, SPECIAL_SPLIT_VERTICAL, SPECIAL_SPLIT_HORIZONTAL, SPECIAL_MAXIMIZE, SPECIAL_MINIMIZE, SPECIAL_FULLSCREEN, SPECIAL_KEEP_ABOVE, SPECIAL_KEEP_BELOW, SPECIAL_NO_TITLEBAR_AND_FRAME, SPECIAL_CLOSE, SPECIAL_EMPTY, SPECIAL_AUTO_TILER_TOGGLE, SPECIAL_AUTO_TILER_1, SPECIAL_AUTO_TILER_2 and SPECIAL_AUTO_TILER_3.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
       </item>
      </layout>
     </widget>
