          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="label_81">
            <property name="text">
             <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Configurations used for auto tiling. Three different auto tiling configurations are possible if you want to use different config on different monitors, virtual desktops or simply toggle between them. Only one configuration can be used on same screen + virtual desktop + activity at a time - if you try to mix them, the new configuration replaces the old one. You can view instructions, predefined layouts (including pictures to give you an idea what each one does) and user submitted layouts &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/rxappdev/MouseTiler/blob/main/AUTOTILERGUIDE.md&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; text-decoration: underline; color:#5294e2;&quot;&gt;here&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="openExternalLinks">
