          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="label_82">
            <property name="text">
             <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Format is same as Popup Grid Layouts. One layout per line. Each line needs to have minimum X tiles where X is the line number. Each tile needs to be prefixed with priority index starting at 0: on line 1. Negative values are allowed to show windows at end of the list. Line 8 needs tiles 0: and 7 other tiles ranging from -6: to 7: (8 numbers including 0). Special tile *: can be used to create fixed tiles. *: tiles will not be be re-prioritized and are simply there to allow mixed auto and normal layout. Place *: in same spot on each layout for best experience.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
