             <property name="text">
              <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;❤   &lt;/span&gt;Thank you for using this tiler!&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;   ❤&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy it and maybe also &lt;a href=&quot;https://store.kde.org/p/2324743&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; text-decoration: underline; color:#5294e2;&quot;&gt;Remember Window Positions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I would really apreciate if you could support me in one way or another.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I have by now spent around 5 months (full time, 8+ hours of work a day) developing these two scripts, and I need to feed myself, my 4 year old son, and pay rent. Sadly donations are scarce (not even covering a single months rent. I am around $5000 behind by now).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Starting February 1st 2026, I will stop adding new features to the scripts, only fixing bugs. This is because I need to do work that earns money so I do not go bankrupt. If the donations ever take off, I will continue with the script development.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;❤   &lt;/span&gt;Thank you - Rafael&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight:700; color:#ff0000;&quot;&gt;   ❤&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
             </property>
             <property name="alignment">
              <set>Qt::AlignmentFlag::AlignLeading|Qt::AlignmentFlag::AlignLeft|Qt::AlignmentFlag::AlignVCenter</set>
