                <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can support me by:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;   Donating - even a small donation goes a long way (links below)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;   Leaving a &lt;a href=&quot;https://store.kde.org/p/2334027&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; text-decoration: underline; color:#5294e2;&quot;&gt;review&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;   Downloading some of my &lt;a href=&quot;https://rxweb.epizy.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; text-decoration: underline; color:#5294e2;&quot;&gt;free games&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
